21
00:02:51.000 --> 00:03:00.000
To do this, go to Preferences, Display, Viewport 2.0, and select DirectX11.

22
00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:05.000
In the script editor, paste the entire script in a new Python window.

23
00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:13.000
Assign the root directory to point to the DNA calibration folder and then execute the entire script.

24
00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:18.000
